        "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\nDrawDB supports many languages, but Assamese (as) is currently missing.\nAssamese-speaking users cannot use the application in their native language, which reduces accessibility and localization coverage.\n\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\nAdd full Assamese language support to the i18n system.\nThis includes:\n\nAdding a new as.js locale file\n\nRegistering Assamese in i18n.js\n\nEnsuring it appears in the language selector\n\nI am willing to contribute the full translation.",
